00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:06.000
"Budhist" ligner, naturligvis, "Ateist" meget.

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:07.000
(Latter)

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:09.000
Men du kommer tilbage som en and.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:15.000
